textfsm_template:
Value VLAN_ID (\S+)
Value MAC_ADDRESS ([0-9a-fA-F:]+)
Value INTERFACE (\S+)
Value STATUS (\S+)
Value TTL (\d+)

Start
  ^\s*--- -> Start_record

Start_record
  ^${VLAN_ID}\s+${MAC_ADDRESS}\s+${INTERFACE}\s+${STATUS}\s+${TTL} -> Record
  ^\s*$$
  ^. -> Error
